Very simple Arduino sketch for the RDA5807M (RRD-102 module) FM radio receiver IC

Original code was written by  

Luc Small  
lucsmall.com  
20150518  

There are lots of BITs undefined in the code. Those bits will be re-defined and added in the comments in the code.

RDA5802E  
RDA5802ES  
RDA5802HS  
RDA5807FP  
RDA5807HS  
RDA5807M  
RDA5807MP  
RDA5807MS  
RDA5807M_RRD-102V2  
RDA5807P  
